quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  12,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  12,1,Alif Laaam Raa yeh kitaab roshan ki ayatain hain
  12,2,hum ne is quran ko arabi mein nazilkiya hai taakay tum samajh sakuu
  12,3,( ae paighambar ) hum is quran ke zariye se jo hum ne tumhari taraf bheja hai tumhe aik nihayat acha qissa sunaate hain aur tum is se pehlay be khabar they
  12,4,jab Yousuf ne apne waalid se kaha ke abba mein ne ( khawab mein ) gayarah sitaron aur Sooraj aur chaand ko dekha hai. daikhta (kiya ) hon ke woh mujhe sajda kar rahay hain
  12,5,unhon ne kaha ke beta apne khawab ka zikar apne bhaiyon se nah karna nahi to woh tumahray haq mein koi fraib ki chaal chalein ge. kuch shak nahi ke shetan ensaan ka khula dushman hai
  12,6,"aur isi terhan khuda tumhe bargzida ( o mumtaaz ) kere ga aur ( khawab ki ) baton ki tabeer ka ilm sikhayiye ga. aur jis terhan is ne apni Nemat pehlay tumahray dada, pardada ibrahim aur Ishaq par poori ki thi isi terhan tum par aur aulaad Yaqoob par poori kere ga. be shak tumhara perwar-digaar ( sab kuch ) jan-nay wala ( aur ) hikmat wala hai"
  12,7,haan Yousuf aur un ke bhaiyon ( ke qissay ) mein poochnay walon ke liye ( bohat si ) nishanain hain
  12,8,jab unhon ne ( aapas mein ) tazkarakiya ke Yousuf aur is ka bhai abba ko hum se ziyada pyare hain halaank hum jamaat ( ki jamaat ) hain. kuch shak nahi ke abba Sarih ghalti par hain
  12,9,to Yousuf ko ( ya to jaan se ) maar daalo ya kisi malik mein pheink aao. phir abba ki tavajja sirf tumhari taraf hojaye gi. aur is ke baad tum achi haalat mein hojao ge
  12,10,un mein se aik kehnay walay ne kaha ke Yousuf ko jaan se nah maro kisi gehray kunvey mein daal do ke koi rahgir nikaal ( kar aur malik mein ) le jaye ga. agar tum ko karna hai ( to yun karo )
  12,11,( yeh mahswara kar ke woh Yaqoob se ) kehnay lagey ke abba jaan kiya sabab hai ke aap Yousuf ke baray mein hamara aitbaar nahi karte halaank hum is ke khair khwah hain
  12,12,kal usay hamaray sath bhaij dijiye ke khoob meway khaye aur khailay kode. hum is ke nigehbaan hain
  12,13,unhon ne kaha ke yeh amar mujhe ghumnaak kiye deta hai ke tum usay le jao ( yani woh mujh se judda hojaye ) aur mujhe yeh khauf bhi hai ke tum ( khail mein ) is se ghaafil hojao aur usay bheria kha jaye
  12,14,"woh kehnay lagey ke agar hamari mojoodgi mein ke hum aik taaqatwar jamaat hain, usay bheria kha gaya to hum barray nuqsaan mein prhgye"
  12,15,gharz jab woh is ko le gay aur is baat par ittafaq karliya ke is ko gehray kunvey mein daal den. to hum ne Yousuf ki taraf wahi bhaije ke ( aik waqt aisa aeye ga ke ) tum un ke is sulooq se aagah karo ge aur un ko ( is wahi ki ) kuch khabar nah hogi
  12,16,( yeh harkat karkay ) woh raat ke waqt baap ke paas rotay hue aeye
  12,17,( aur ) kehnay lagey ke abba jaan hum to dornay aur aik dosray se agay niklny mein masroof hogaye aur Yousuf ko apne asbaab ke paas chore gay to usay bheria kha gaya. aur aap hamari baat ko go hum sach hi kehte hon bawar nahi karen ge
  12,18,aur un ke karte par jhoot moot ka lahoo bhi laga laaye. Yaqoob ne kaha ( ke haqeeqat haal yun nahi hai ) balkay tum apne dil se ( yeh ) baat bana laaye ho. acha sabr ( ke wohi ) khoob ( hai ) aur jo tum bayan karte ho is ke baray mein khuda hi se madad matloob hai
  12,19,( ab khuda ki shaan dekho ke is kunvey ke qareeb ) aik qaafla آوارد howa aur unhon ne ( pani ke liye ) apna saqqa bheja. is ne kunvey mein doll latkaya ( to Yousuf is se latak gay ) woh bola zahe qismat yeh to ( nihayat Hussain ) larka hai. aur is ko qeemti sarmaya samajh kar chhupa liya aur jo kuch woh karte they khuda ko sab maloom tha
  12,20,aur is ko thori si qeemat ( yani ) madode(sirf) chand darhamon par beech dala. aur inhen un ( ke baray ) mein kuch lalach nah tha
  12,21,aur misar mein jis shakhs ne is ko khareeda is ne apni biwi se ( jis ka naam zulekha tha ) kaha ke is ko izzat wa karam se rakho ajab nahi ke yeh hamein faida day ya hum usay beta banalen. is terhan hum ne Yousuf ko sarzamen ( misar ) mein jagah di aur gharz yeh thi ke hum un ko ( khawab ki ) baton ki tabeer skhayin aur khuda apne kaam par ghalib hai lekin aksar log nahi jantay
  12,22,aur jab woh apni jawani ko puhanche to hum ne un ko danai aur ilm bakhsha. aur naiko karon ko hum isi terhan badla diya karte hain
  12,23,to jis aurat ke ghar mein woh rehtay they is ne un ko apni taraf mael karna chaha aur darwazay band karkay kehnay lagi ( Yousuf ) jaldi aao. unhon ne kaha ke khuda panah mein rakhay ( woh yani tumahray miyan ) to mere aaqa hain unhon ne mujhe achi terhan se rakha hai ( mein aisa zulm nahi karsaktha ) be shak zalim log Falah nahi payen ge
  12,24,aur is aurat ne un ka qasadkiya aur unhon ne is ka qasadkiya. agar woh apne perwar-digaar ki nishani nah dekhte ( to jo hota hota ) yun is liye (kiya gaya ) ke hum un se buraiee aur be hiyai ko rok den. be shak woh hamaray khalis bundon mein se they
  12,25,aur dono darwazay ki taraf bhage ( agay Yousuf aur peechay zulekha ) aur aurat ne un ka karta peechay se ( pakar kar jo khincha to ) phaar dala aur dono ko darwazay ke paas aurat ka khawand mil gaya to aurat boli ke jo shakhs tumhari biwi ke sath bura iradah kere is ki is ke siwakiya saza hai ke ya to qaidkiya jaye ya dukh ka azaab diya jaye
  12,26,Yousuf ne kaha isi ne mujh ko apni taraf mael karna chaha tha. is ke qabeeley mein se aik faisla karne walay ne faislakiya ke agar is ka karta agay se phataa to yeh sachhi aur Yousuf jhoota
  12,27,aur agar karta peechay se phataa ho to yeh jhooti aur woh sacha hai
  12,28,aur jab is ka karta dekha ( to ) peechay se phataa tha ( tab is ne zulekha se kaha ) ke yeh tumhara hi fraib hai. aur kuch shak nahi ke tum aurton ke fraib barray ( bhaari ) hotay hain
  12,29,"Yousuf is baat ka khayaal nah kar. aur ( zulekha ) to apne gunaaho ki bakhshish maang, be shak khata teri hai"
  12,30,aur shehar mein aurtain gftgoyin karne lagen ke Aziz ki biwi apne ghulam ko apni taraf mael karna chahti hai. aur is ki mohabbat is ke dil mein ghar kar gayi hai. hum dekhatii hain ke woh Sarih gumraahi mein hai
  12,31,jab zulekha ne un aurton ki ( guftagu jo haqeeqat mein deedar Yousuf ke liye aik ) chaal ( thi ) suni to un ke paas ( dawat ka ) pegham bheja aur un ke liye aik mehfhil muratab ki. aur ( phal taraashney ke liye ) har aik ko aik churee di aur ( Yousuf se ) kaha ke un ke samnay bahar aao. jab aurton ne un ko dekha to un ka roab ( husn ) un par ( aisa ) chhaa gaya ke ( phal tarashtain tarashtain ) apne haath kaat liye aur be sakhta bol utheen ke subhan allah ( yeh husn ) yeh aadmi nahi koi buzurag farishta hai
  12,32,tab zulekha ne kaha yeh wohi hai jis ke baray mein tum mujhe taanay deti theen. aur be shak mein ne is ko apni taraf mael karna chaha magar yeh bacha raha. aur agar yeh woh kaam nah kere ga jo mein usay kehti hon to qaid kardiya jaye ga aur zaleel hoga
  12,33,Yousuf ne dua ki ke perwar-digaar jis kaam ki taraf yeh mujhe bulati hain is ki nisbat mujhe qaid pasand hai. aur agar to mujh se un ke fraib ko nah htaye ga to mein un ki taraf mael hojaon ga aur nadanon mein daakhil hojaon ga
  12,34,to khuda ne un ki dua qubool karli aur un se aurton ka makr dafaa kar diya. be shak woh suneney ( aur ) jan-nay wala hai
  12,35,phir bawajood is ke ke woh log nishaan dekh chuke they un ki raye yahi thahri ke kuch arsa ke liye un ko qaid hi kar dein
  12,36,aur un ke sath do aur jawan bhi daakhil zndan hue. aik ne un mein se kaha ke ( mein ne khawab dekha hai ) daikhta (kiya ) hon ke sharaab ( ke liye angoor ) nichor raha hon. dosray ne kaha ke ( mein ne bhi khawab dekha hai ) mein yeh daikhta hon ke apne sir par rotian uthaye hue hon aur janwar un mein se kha rahay ( hain to ) hamein un ki tabeer bta dijiye ke hum tumhe nekokaar dekhte hain
  12,37,Yousuf ne kaha ke jo khana tum ko milnay wala hai woh anay nahi paye ga ke mein is se pehlay tum ko is ki tabeer btadon ga. yeh un ( baton ) mein se hai jo mere perwar-digaar ne mujhe sikhayi hain jo log khuda par imaan nahi laatay aur roz akhirat se inkaar karte hain mein un ka mazhab chhorey hue hon
  12,38,aur apne baap dada ibrahim aur Ishaq aur Yaqoob ke mazhab par chalta hon. hamein Shayaan nahi hai ke kisi cheez ko khuda ke sath shareek banayen. yeh khuda ka fazl hai hum par bhi aur logon par bhi hai lekin aksar log shukar nahi karte
  12,39,mere jail khanaay ke rafiqo! bhala kayi judda judda aaqa achay ya ( aik ) khuday-e yaktaa o ghalib ?
  12,40,jin cheezon ki tum khuda ke siwa parastish karte ho woh sirf naam hi naam hain jo tum ne aur tumahray baap dada ne rakh liye hain. khuda ne un ki koi sanad nazil nahi ki. ( sun rakho ke ) khuda ke siwa kisi ki hukoomat nahi hai. is ne irshad farmaya hai ke is ke siwa kisi ki ibadat nah karo. yahi seedha deen hai lekin aksar log nahi jantay
  12,41,mere jail khanaay ke rafiqo! tum mein se aik ( jo pehla khawab bayan karne wala hai woh ) to apne aaqa ko sharaab pilaya kere ga aur jo dosra hai woh suli diya jaye ga aur janwar is ka sir kha jayen ge. jo amar tum mujh se puchhte they woh faisla hochuka hai
  12,42,aur dono shakhson mein se jis ki nisbat ( Yousuf ne ) khayaalkiya ke woh rihayi pa jaye ga is se kaha ke apne aaqa se mera zikar bhi karna lekin shetan ne un ka apne aaqa se zikar karna bhala diya aur Yousuf kayi baras jail khanaay mein rahay
  12,43,aur badshah ne kaha ke mein ( ne khawab dekha hai ) daikhta (kiya ) hon ke saat mouti ghaein hain jin ko saat dubli ghaein kha rahi hain aur saatkhoshay sabz hain aur ( saat ) khushk. ae sardaro ! agar tum khowaboon ki tabeer day satke ho to mujhe mere khawab ki tabeer batao
  12,44,unhon ne kaha yeh to pareshan se khawab hain. aur hamein aisay khowaboon ki tabeer nahi aati
  12,45,ab woh shakhs jo dono qaidyoun mein se rihayi pa gaya tha aur jisay muddat ke baad woh baat yaad aagai bol utha ke mein aap ko is ki tabeer ( laa ) batata hon mujhe ( jail khanaay ) jaane ki ijazat day dijiye
  12,46,( gharz woh Yousuf ke paas aaya aur kehnay laga ) Yousuf ae barray sachey ( Yousuf ) hamein is khawab ki tabeer bataiyay ke saat mouti gayyon ko saat dubli ghaein kha rahi hain. aur saat khoshay sabz hain aur saat sokhey taakay mein logon ke paas wapas ja ( kar tabeer batau ). ajab nahi ke woh ( tumhari qader ) jaanen
  12,47,unhon ne kaha ke tum log saat saal mutawatar khaiti karte rahoge to jo ( Ghalla ) katu to thoray se ghallay ke siwa jo khanay mein aeye usay khoshon mein hi rehne dena
  12,48,phir is ke baad ( khushk saali ke ) saat sakht ( saal ) ayen ge ke jo ( Ghalla ) tum ne jama kar rakha hoga woh is sab ko kha jayen ge. sirf wohi thora sa reh jaye ga jo tum ahthyat se rakh chhorro ge
  12,49,phir is ke baad aik saal aeye ga ke khoob meen barsay ga aur log is mein ras nachorain ge
  12,50,( yeh tabeer sun kar ) badshah ne hukum diya ke Yousuf ko mere paas le aao. jab qasid un ke paas gaya to unhon ne kaha ke apne aaqa ke paas wapas jao aur un se pucho ke un aurton kakiya haal hai jinhon ne apne haath kaat liye they. be shak mera perwar-digaar un ke makaron se khoob waaqif hai
  12,51,badshah ne aurton se poocha ke bhala is waqtkiya howa tha jab tum ne Yousuf ko apni taraf mael karna chaha. sab bol utheen ke Hash allah(masha Allah) hum ne is mein koi buraiee maloom nahi ki. Aziz ki aurat ne kaha ab sachhi baat to zahir ho hi gayi hai. ( asal yeh hai ke ) mein ne is ko apni taraf mael karna chaha tha aur be shak woh sacha hai
  12,52,( Yousuf ne kaha ke mein ne ) yeh baat is liye ( poochi hai ) ke Aziz ko yaqeen hojaye ke mein ne is ki peeth peechay is ki ( amanat mein khayanat nahi ki ) aur khuda khayanat karne walon ke makro ko robarah (kamyab) nahi karta
  12,53,aur mein apne tain pak saaf nahi kehta kyunkay nafs amarh ( ensaan ko ) buraiee sakata rehta hai. magar yeh ke mera perwar-digaar reham kere ga. be shak mera perwar-digaar bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  12,54,badshah ne hukum diya ke usay mere paas lao mein usay apna musahib khaas bunun ga. phir jab un se guftagu ki to kaha ke aaj se tum hamaray haan sahib manzilat aur sahib aitbaar ho
  12,55,( Yousuf ne ) kaha mujhe is malik ke khazanon par muqarrar kar dijiye kyunkay mein hifazat bhi karsaktha hon aur is kaam se waaqif hon
  12,56,is terhan hum ne Yousuf ko malik ( misar ) mein jagah di aur woh is malik mein jahan chahtay they rehtay they. hum apni rehmat jis par chahtay hain karte hain aur naiko karon ke ajar ko zaya nahi karte
  12,57,aur jo log imaan laaye aur drtay rahay un ke liye akhirat ka ajar bohat behtar hai
  12,58,aur Yousuf ke bhai ( canaan se misar mein Ghalla kharidne ke liye ) aeye to Yousuf ke paas gay to Yousuf ne un ko pehchan liya aur woh un ko nah pehchan sakay
  12,59,jab Yousuf ne un ke liye un ka samaan tayyar kar diya to kaha ke ( phir aana to ) jo baap ki taraf se tumhara aik aur bhai hai usay bhi mere paas letay aana.kiya tum nahi dekhte ke mein naap bhi poori poori deta hon aur mhmandari bhi khoob karta hon
  12,60,aur agar tum usay mere paas nah lao ge to nah tumhe mere haan se Ghalla miley ga aur nah tum mere paas hi aa sako ge
  12,61,unhon ne kaha ke hum is ke baray mein is ke waalid se tazkara karen ge aur hum ( yeh kaam ) karkay rahen ge
  12,62,( aur Yousuf ne ) apne Khudam se kaha ke un ka sarmaya ( yani ghallay ki qeemat ) un ke shaliton mein rakh do ajab nahi ke jab yeh apne ahal vayal mein jayen to usay pehchan len ( aur ) ajab nahi ke phir yahan ayen
  12,63,jab woh apne baap ke paas wapas gay to kehnay lagey ke abba ( jab taq hum Binyamin ko sath nah le jayen ) hamaray liye ghallay ki bandish kar di gayi hai to hamaray sath hamaray bhai ko bhaij day taakay hum phir Ghalla layein aur hum is ke nigehbaan hain
  12,64,( Yaqoob ne ) kaha ke mein is ke baray mein tumhara aitbaar nahi karta magar waisa hi jaissa is ke bhai ke baray meinkiya tha. so khuda hi behtar nigehbaan hai. aur woh sab se ziyada reham karne wala hai
  12,65,aur jab unhon ne apna asbaab khoola to dekha ke un ka sarmaya wapas kar diya gaya hai. kehnay lagey abba hamein ( aur )kiya chahiye ( dekhieye ) yeh hamari poonji bhi hamein wapas kar di gayi hai. ab hum apne ahal vayal ke liye phir Ghalla layein ge aur apne bhai ki nigehbani karen ge aur aik baar shutar ziyada layein ge ( ke ) yeh Ghalla jo hum laaye hain thora hai
  12,66,( Yaqoob ne ) kaha jab taq tum khuda ka ehad nah do ke is ko mere paas ( sahih salim ) le aao ge mein usay hargiz tumahray sath nahi bhejnay ka. magar yeh ke tum ghair liye jao ( yani be bas hojao to majaboori hai ) jab unhon ne un se ehad karliya to ( Yaqoob ne ) kaha ke jo qowl o qarar hum kar rahay hain is ka khuda zamin hai
  12,67,aur hadaayat ki ke beta aik hi darwazay se daakhil nah hona balkay judda judda darwazon se daakhil hona. aur mein khuda ki taqdeer ko tum se nahi rok sakta. be shak hukum isi ka hai mein isi par bharosa rakhta hon. aur ehley tawakkal ko isi par bharosa rakhna chahiye
  12,68,aur jab woh un un maqamat se daakhil hue jahan jahan se ( daakhil honay ke liye ) baap ne un se kaha tha to woh tadbeer khuda ke hukum ko zara bhi nahi taall sakti thi haan woh Yaqoob ke dil ki khwahish thi jo unhon ne poori ki thi. aur be shak woh sahib ilm they kyunkay hum ne un ko ilm sikhaya tha lekin aksar log nahi jantay
  12,69,aur jab woh log Yousuf ke paas puhanche to Yousuf ne apne haqeeqi bhai ko apne paas jagah di aur kaha ke mein tumhara bhai hon to jo sulooq yeh ( hamaray sath ) karte rahay hain is par afsos nah karna
  12,70,jab un ka asbaab tayyar kar diya to apne bhai ke shaltite mein (saman mein) glass rakh diya aur phir ( jab woh abadi se bahar nikal gay to ) aik pukarnay walay ne aawaz di ke qaafley walo tum to chor ho
  12,71,woh un ki taraf mutwajjah ho kar kehnay lagey tumharikiya cheez khoyi gayi hai
  12,72,woh bolay ke badshah ( ke pani peenay ) ka glass khoya gaya hai aur jo shakhs is ko le aeye is ke liye aik baar shutar ( inaam ) aur mein is ka zamin hon
  12,73,woh kehnay lagey ke khuda ki qasam tum ko maloom hai ke hum ( is ) malik mein is liye nahi aeye ke kharabi karen aur nah hum chorikiya karte hain
  12,74,bolay ke agar tum jhutay niklay ( yani chori saabit hui ) to is ki sazakiya
  12,75,unhon ne kaha ke is ki saza yeh hai ke jis ke shaltite mein (saman mein) woh dastyab ho wohi is ka badal qarar diya jaye hum zaalmon ko yahi saza diya karte hain
  12,76,phir Yousuf ne apne bhai ke shalite (saman) se pehlay un ke shaliton (saman) ko dekhna shurukiya phir apne bhai ke shaltite mein (saman mein) se is ko nikaal liya. is terhan hum ne Yousuf ke liye tadbeer ki ( warna ) badshah ke qanoon ke mutabiq woh mushiyat khuda ke siwa apne bhai ko le nahi satke they. hum jis ke liye chahtay hain darjay buland karte hain. aur har ilm walay se dosra ilm wala barh kar hai
  12,77,( baradran Yousuf ne ) kaha ke agar is ne chori ki ho to ( kuch ajab nahi ke ) is ke aik bhai ne bhi pehlay chori ki thi Yousuf ne is baat ko apne dil mein makhfi rakha aur un par zahir nah honay diya ( aur ) kaha ke tum barray bad-qamash ho. aur jo tum bayan karte ho khuda usay khoob jaanta hai
  12,78,woh kehnay lagey ke ae Aziz is ke waalid bohat boorhay hain ( aur is se bohat mohabbat rakhtay hain ) to ( is ko chore degiye aur ) is ki jagah hum mein se kisi ko rakh lijiye. hum dekhte hain ke aap ahsaan karne walay hain
  12,79,( Yousuf ne ) kaha ke khuda panah mein rakhay ke jis shakhs ke paas hum ne apni cheez payi hai is ke siwa kisi aur ko pakar len aisa karen to hum ( barray ) be insaaf hain
  12,80,jab woh is se na umeed hogaye to allag ho kar Salah karne lagey. sab se barray ne kahakiya tum nahi jantay ke tumahray waalid ne tum se khuda ka ehad liya hai aur is se pehlay bhi tum Yousuf ke baray mein qasoor kar chuke ho to jab taq waalid sahib mujhe hukum nah den mein to is jagah se hilnay ka nahi ya khuda mere liye koi aur tadbeer kere. aur woh sab se behtar faisla karne wala hai
  12,81,tum sab waalid sahib ke paas wapas jao aur kaho ke abba aap ke sahibzaday ne ( wahan ja kar ) chori ki. aur hum ne apni Danist ke mutabiq aap se ( is ke le anay ka ) ehadkiya tha magar hum ghaib ki baton ko jan-nay aur yaad rakhnay walay to nahi they
  12,82,aur jis bastii mein hum ( thehray ) they wahan se ( yani ahal misar se ) aur jis qaafley mein aeye hain is se daryaft kar lijiye aur hum is bayan mein bilkul sachey hain
  12,83,( jab unhon ne yeh baat Yaqoob se aa kar kahi to ) unhon ne kaha ke ( haqeeqat yun nahi hai ) balkay yeh baat tum ne apne dil se banali hai to sabr hi behtar hai. ajab nahi ke khuda un sab ko mere paas le aeye. be shak woh Dana ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  12,84,phir un ke paas se chalay gay aur kehnay lagey haae afsos Yousuf ( haae afsos ) aur ranj والم mein ( is qader roye ke ) un ki ankhen safaid hogyin aur un ka dil gham se bhar raha tha
  12,85,betay kehnay lagey ke ﻭﺍﻟﻠﻪ agar aap Yousuf ko isi terhan yaad hi karte rahen ge to ya to bemaar ho jaien ge ya jaan hi day den ge
  12,86,unhon ne kaha ke mein apne gham واندوہ ka izhaar khuda se karta hon. aur khuda ki taraf se woh baatein jaanta hon jo tum nahi jantay
  12,87,beta ( yun karo ke aik dafaa phir ) jao aur Yousuf aur is ke bhai ko talaash karo aur khuda ki rehmat se na umeed nah ho. ke khuda ki rehmat se be imaan log na umeed howa karte hain
  12,88,jab woh Yousuf ke paas gay to kehnay lagey ke Aziz hamein aur hamaray ahal vayal ko barri takleef ho rahi hai aur hum thora sa sarmaya laaye hain aap hamein ( is ke aiwz ) poora Ghalla day dijiye aur khairaat kijiye. ke khuda khairaat karne walon ko sawab deta hai
  12,89,( Yousuf ne ) kaha tumhe maloom hai jab tum nadani mein phansay hue they to tum ne Yousuf aur is ke bhai ke sathkiyakiya tha
  12,90,woh bolaykiya tum hi Yousuf ho? unhon ne kaha haan mein hi Yousuf hon. aur ( Binyamin ki taraf ishara karkay kehnay lagey ) yeh mera bhai hai khuda ne hum par bara ahsaankiya hai. jo shakhs khuda se darta aur sabr karta hai to khuda naiko karon ka ajar zaya nahi karta
  12,91,woh bolay khuda ki qasam khuda ne tum ko hum par fazeelat bakhsh hai aur be shak hum khatakaar they
  12,92,( Yousuf ne ) kaha ke aaj ke din se tum par kuch Atab ( وملامت ) nahi hai. khuda tum ko maaf kere. aur woh bohat reham karne wala hai
  12,93,yeh mera kurta le jao aur usay waalid sahib ke munh par daal do. woh Beena ho jayen ge. aur apne tamam ahal vayal ko mere paas le aao
  12,94,aur jab qaafla ( misar se ) rawana howa to un ke waalid kehnay lagey ke agar mujh ko yeh nah kaho ke ( boorha ) behak gaya hai to mujhe to Yousuf ki bo aa rahi hai
  12,95,woh bolay ke wallah aap isi qadeem ghalti mein ( mubtala ) hain
  12,96,jab khushkhabri dainay wala aa pouncha to kurta Yaqoob ke munh par daal diya aur woh Beena ho gay ( aur beiton se ) kehnay lageykiya mein ne tum se nahi kaha tha ke mein khuda ki taraf se woh baatein jaanta hon jo tum nahi jantay
  12,97,beiton ne kaha ke abba hamaray liye hamaray gunah ki mughfirat mangi-ye. be shak hum khatakaar they
  12,98,unhon ne kaha ke mein apne perwar-digaar se tumahray liye bakhshish maanguu ga. be shak woh bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  12,99,jab yeh ( sab log ) Yousuf ke paas puhanche to Yousuf ne apne walidain ko apne paas bithaya aur kaha misar mein daakhil ho jaiye khuda ne chaha to jama khatir se rhiye ga
  12,100,aur apne walidain ko takhat par bithaya aur sab yousuf ke agay sajda mein gir parre aur ( is waqt ) Yousuf ne kaha abba jaan yeh mere is khawab ki tabeer hai jo mein ne pehlay ( bachpan mein ) dekha tha. mere perwar-digaar ne usay sach kar dekhaya aur is ne mujh par ( bohat se ) ahsaan kiye hain ke mujh ko jail khanaay se nikala. aur is ke baad ke shetan ne mujh mein aur mere bhaiyon mein fasaad daal diya tha. aap ko gaon se yahan laya. be shak mera perwar-digaar jo chahta hai tadbeer se karta hai. woh Dana ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  12,101,( jab yeh sab baatein holin to Yousuf ne khuda se dua ki ke ) ae mere perwar-digaar to ne mujh ko hukoomat se behra diya aur khowaboon ki tabeer ka ilm bakhsha. ae asmano aur zameen ke peda karne walay to hi duniya aur akhirat mein mera karsaaz hai. to mujhe ( duniya se ) apni itaat ( ki haalat ) mein اٹھائیو aur ( akhirat mein ) apne naik bundon mein daakhil kejio
  12,102,( ae paighambar ) yeh akhbar ghaib mein se hain jo hum tumhari taraf bhaijtay hain aur jab baradran Yousuf ne apni baat par ittafaqkiya tha aur woh fraib kar rahay they to tum un ke paas to nah they
  12,103,aur bohat se aadmi go tum ( kitni hi ) khwahish karo imaan laane walay nahi hain
  12,104,aur tum un se is ( kher khawahi ) ka kuch sla bhi to nahi mangte. yeh quran aur kuch nahi tamam aalam ke liye nasiyaat hai
  12,105,aur aasman o zameen mein bohat si nishanain hain jin par yeh guzarte hain aur un se aaraiz karte hain
  12,106,aur yeh aksar khuda par imaan nahi rakhtay. magar ( is ke sath ) shirk karte hain
  12,107,kiya yeh is ( baat ) se be khauf hain ke un par khuda ka azaab nazil ho kar un ko dhaanp le ya un par nagahan qayamat aajay aur inhen khabar bhi nah ho
  12,108,keh do mera rasta to yeh hai mein khuda ki taraf bulaataa hon ( az roye yaqeen وبرہان ) samajh boojh kar mein bhi ( logon ko khuda ki taraf bulaataa hon ) aur mere pairo bhi. aur khuda pak hai. aur mein shirk karne walon mein se nahi hon
  12,109,aur hum ne tum se pehlay bustiyon ke rehne walon mein se mard hi beje they jin ki taraf hum wahi bhaijtay they.kiya un logon ne malik mein sair ( vsyaht ) nahi ki ke dekh letay ke jo log un se pehlay they un ka injaamkiya howa. aur متقیوں ke liye akhirat ka ghar bohat acha hai.kiya tum samajte nahi ?
  12,110,yahan taq ke jab paighambar na umeed hogaye aur unhon ne khayaalkiya ke apni nusrat ke baray mein jo baat unhon ne kahi thi ( is mein ) woh sachey nah niklay to un ke paas hamari madad aa pohanchi. phir jisay hum ne chaha bacha diya. aur hamara azaab ( utar kar ) gunehgaar logon se phira nahi karta
  12,111,un ke qissay mein aqalmandon ke liye Ibrat hai. yeh ( quran ) aisi baat nahi hai jo ( apne dil se ) banai gayi ho balkay jo ( kitaaben ) is se pehlay nazil hui hain un ki tasdeeq ( karne wala ) hai aur mominoun ke liye hadaayat aur rehmat hai
